INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES (74,'一个男人怎么样算是有趣','<span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">1.有点害羞，但曾在分手的街头，大声的说我爱你。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">2.同我去庙里求签，轻轻的捉住我的手一同跪下。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">3.言而有信。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">4.从来不迟到–我迟到他不生气。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">5.拥抱很久，很紧—每次我起身时几乎是需要慢慢推开他。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">6.睡得比我迟一点，醒来早一点。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">7.朦胧醒来轻呼我的名字–没有呼错。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">8.记得我的日期，鞋号，密码，最怕的事。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">9.我很怕虫子，见到虫子大声尖叫他不会笑我。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">10.雨后的早晨我去花园，用小树枝把爬到路上来的蚯蚓送还草地–他在一边帮我。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">11.笑起来很象个坏蛋–其实不是。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">12.不舒服时，请假带我看医生，回来的路上买冰淇淋做奖励。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">13.开车绝不喝酒，让我系上安全带。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">14.帮我做家务，每天。边做边聊天。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">15.常常帮助别人，不为什么。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">16.答应我：永远不。然后永远不。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">17.一边吹口哨一边修马桶。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">18.说：希望你是我女儿。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">19.白煮蛋的黄可以给他吃。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">20.雨天散步，背我过积水，说：你还可以再胖一些。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">21.吵嘴时不会一走了之。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">22.错了会认错。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">23.阅读女士脱毛器的说明书然后教我。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">24.我说笑话他笑。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">25.逛街时我看中同一款三种颜色的裙子，他说：都试一遍好了。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">26.试鞋时，他把我的卡通袜叠叠塞进上衣口袋。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">27.常常说，有我呢。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">28.事情过了以后才告诉我，轻描淡写。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">29.指甲整齐干净，喜欢我替他剪指甲。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">30.我做的菜他每样都爱吃，要求明天再做。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">31.小孩子都喜欢他，常常在楼下玩一裤子泥回来。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">32.轻轻拧开我拧不开的汽水瓶。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">33.忙时替我订机票，让我带父母一起出去玩。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">34.告诉我–24小时随时打电话。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">35.告诉我–不要省钱。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">36.去义务献血，回来笑嘻嘻掏出一块“福利饼干”给我尝</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">37.偷偷买一件两人合穿的雨衣放在车上。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">38.我喜欢赤脚，他在副驾驶位脚下铺块小羊绒毯。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">39.留言时画一个小老虎头当签名。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">40.偶尔叫我妈妈。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">41.说谎时结巴。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">42.与人争论时听上去像解释。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">43.教我滑旱冰，扶着我跑了快一千公里。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">44.从不上网聊天。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">45.他的秘书说帮他缝上脱落的纽扣，他说谢谢，不用。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">46.送我的花是盆花，替我浇水。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">47.和我下棋，允许我悔棋。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">48.喜欢运动，带我去招待女宾俱乐部。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">49.穿十年前的牛仔裤依然合身。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">50.他养了一条大狗，他的狗喜欢我。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">51.吵嘴时我要他还我送给他的维尼熊，他坚决不还。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">52.我不辨方向，他体内有指南针，说–跟牢我。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">53.吃我吃剩的东西。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">54.我失眠时他陪我聊天。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">55.能用双肘和膝部支撑体重。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">56.他以前的女友有困难会来找他，没有困难则不会。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">57.手上有道疤–和几个小流氓打架时捏住对方的刀，我警告他下次不要这样了，他点头含笑不语。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">58.我洗澡时他拿了本杂志进来坐在马桶上看。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">59.比我高，我取不到的东西让他取。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">60.重大的事情和我商量，比如明年的投资计划，周末野餐带不带烧烤架，晚上吃大白菜还是小白菜。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">61.站在商店的洗手间外面等我。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">62.我感冒了，他还是用我的杯子喝水。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">63.打电话嚷：我办公室的热带鱼生小鱼了！</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">64.和大人在一起像大人，和孩子在一起像孩子，和狗在一起像狗。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">65.钱不会多到要别的女人替他花。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">66.喜欢我，从未犹豫，从不和别的女人比较。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">67.必须非常合心的东西才买—没时从不问价格，然后用很久很久。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">68.火车站接我，早到十分钟，带一盒草莓酸奶。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">69.常常央求我唱一首歌。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">70.我买给他的东西都合他的心，不转送他人。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">71.身上的味道很好闻，但他自己不知道。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">72.逛街回家，一只眼睛看电视球赛一直眼看我试新衣服。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">73.对女人有风度，也有距离。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">74.有了他，电脑罢工不必彻夜痛苦。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">75.很少叹气。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">76.不想当官。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">77.真的可以随时找到他。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">78.和他在一起不怕死—也不害怕活下去，活到很老。</span>','2014-04-27 19:07:27','2014-05-01 02:23:42'),(77,'使用了七牛提供的免费云加速了博客的静态文件','<p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">上一篇博文说到<a title=\"使用七牛云存储自动增量备份vps数据\" href=\"http://yazi.whoknow.me/%e4%bd%bf%e7%94%a8%e4%b8%83%e7%89%9b%e4%ba%91%e5%ad%98%e5%82%a8%e8%87%aa%e5%8a%a8%e5%a2%9e%e9%87%8f%e5%a4%87%e4%bb%bdvps%e6%95%b0%e6%8d%ae/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">使用七牛提供的免费空间自动备份vps数据</a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">然后就去装了一个我爱水煮鱼写的<a title=\"七牛镜像存储 WordPress 插件：一键实现 WordPress 博客静态文件 CDN 加速\" href=\"http://blog.wpjam.com/project/wpjam-qiniutek/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 